Chai Latte with A Pop3.

Chai Latte is a delicious enriching tea hailing from the Middle East. Easy to make and delicious, Chai will brighten up any morning.

Ingredients.
1 cup milk
1 cup water
1 g orange peel
3 g cloves
1 g cinnamon stick
3 pinches peppercorns
1 pinch nutmeg
4 g sugar
2 g black tea

Method.
Put milk into the 1st teapot.
Liquify contents of the teapot.
Pour contents of the 1st teapot into the baking dish.

Serves 1.